&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/Leafony/HW-Design-Files/blob/master/AP02A_ESP32_MCU/AP02A_ESP32_MCU_Schematic.pdf&#34;&gt;回路図&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
